Module scrabble.main
Package cl.uchile.dcc.scrabble.types.numbers

Class ScrBinary

java.lang.Object
cl.uchile.dcc.scrabble.types.AbstractType
cl.uchile.dcc.scrabble.types.numbers.ScrBinary
All Implemented Interfaces:
LogicalOp, IOperations, SType, java.lang.Comparable<IOperations>
public class ScrBinary
extends AbstractType
implements IOperations, LogicalOp, java.lang.Comparable<IOperations>
The ScrBinary class wraps an String consisting of only '0' and '1' that represents a signed int. A ScrBinary object contains a single field whose type is String, representing a 16-bit binary
